For creating two nodes cluster Kubernetes, It is required to perform the below steps.

##For Master node Perform the below activity 

 1. sudo hostnamectl set-hostname k8_server
 2. sudo vi /etc/hosts : Where you need to add below: 
    172.31.54.12 k8server
    172.31.55.11 worker1

   14  cat << EOF | sudo tee /etc/modules-load.d/containerd.conf
overlay
br_netfilter
>EOF

   15  cat << EOF | sudo tee /etc/modules-load.d/containerd.conf
overlay
br_netfilter
EOF

   16  sudo modprobe overlay
   17  sudo modprobe br_netfilter
   18  cat << EOF | sudo tee /etc/sysctl.d/99-kubernetes.cri.conf
net.bridge.bridge-nf-call-iptables =1
net.ipv4..ip_forward = 1
net.bridge.bridge-nf-call-ip6tables = 1
EOF

   19  sudo sysctl --system
   20  sudo mkdir -p /etc/containerd
